title: Darby's Restaurant and Pub
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Vegetarian dishes are clearly labeled but vegans need to ask. Some of the vegetarian dishes might be vegan or could possibly be made vegan, including zucchini sliders, sweet potato and bean burrito, a rice and vegetable bowl and pad thai. Has gluten free menu. A pub atmosphere with mostly wooden tables with benches or chairs.  There are bars in at least two of the dining rooms.
